name: The Demon Child
description: When I was about 14 years old I smoked some weed that was laced. (Assumed was PCP with the visuals that came with it.) During the first half of that awful experience I was running in the woods. Away from this demon child that was chasing me. I could only see parts of it's face when I would turn to see where the running sounds were coming from hahahahaha awful.
